    {
      "type": "text", "id": "lc_footer_title",
      "x": 100, "y": 1694, "width": 600, "height": 22,
      "text": "🔑 Why the scope split matters — cross-session reuse",
      "originalText": "🔑 Why the scope split matters — cross-session reuse",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e40af", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1200003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1200004,
      "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "lc_footer_body",
      "x": 100, "y": 1722, "width": 1580, "height": 75,
      "text": "Task names are GLOBAL, not session-scoped.  reports/data/col_overview.md is the SAME file across every session — session run1 writes it, run2 reads the cached\nreport and skips re-running (skills check file existence and bail out if >100 bytes).  Result: D/I tasks accumulate across sessions and compose over time.\nSwitching {aim} is cheap — sessions/{aim}/ starts fresh but reports/ and code/ are inherited.  Plan iteration (GO_BACK · ADD_TASKS · REVISE_PLAN) re-runs only new tasks;\nprior reports stay valid.  Gate files (sessions/{aim}/gates/gate_*.md) and DIKW_STATE.json form the audit trail and enable resume-after-compaction.",
      "originalText": "Task names are GLOBAL, not session-scoped.  reports/data/col_overview.md is the SAME file across every session — session run1 writes it, run2 reads the cached\nreport and skips re-running (skills check file existence and bail out if >100 bytes).  Result: D/I tasks accumulate across sessions and compose over time.\nSwitching {aim} is cheap — sessions/{aim}/ starts fresh but reports/ and code/ are inherited.  Plan iteration (GO_BACK · ADD_TASKS · REVISE_PLAN) re-runs only new tasks;\nprior reports stay valid.  Gate files (sessions/{aim}/gates/gate_*.md) and DIKW_STATE.json form the audit trail and enable resume-after-compaction.",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1200005, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1200006,
      "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.45
